\subsubsection*{Sports Addiction}

I pondered on my addiction to following sports.
I read an article by someone who quit following sports.
Here are some thoughts.

\begin{itemize}
 \item The thing I hate about it is having an emotional investment in the
outcome of something to which I have no tangible connection.
\item The other thing which I don't like about it is the time I waste on it.
\item The positive is that it is the great equalizer---I can talk to most any
guy about sports.
\end{itemize}

